widgets_values:
Preferably, use a base image where each dimensions is a multiple of 16
If other dimensions are used, the image will be cropped


Examples:
480x540
576x1024
832x1216

If using landscape aspect ratio, swap the values for width and height in the "Load & Resize Image" node and the "Resize Image" node in the "Prep Video" section.
Increase blocks_to_swap up to 40 to decrease vram

Higher rel_l1_thresh will go faster at the expense of quality
Probably don't go above 0.4
